OL,3,CPolice 'gripped' seriousness of Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe disappearance
OL,6,FPolice "gripped" the seriousness of
OL,7,Fthe investigation into the
OL,8,Fdisappearance of Noah Donohoe at an
OL,9,Fearly stage, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FChief Inspector Robinson told Belfast
OL,12,FCoroner's Court that he had carried
OL,13,Fout a compliance review into how
OL,14,Fpolice carried out their search for
OL,15,Fthe teenager in 2020.
OL,17,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,18,Fschoolboy at Belfast Coroner's Court,
OL,19,Fwhich is being heard with a jury, has
OL,20,Fnow entered its seventh week.
OL,26,@nD@HOUnD@PO]
