OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773144740
OL,3,CPolice 'gripped' seriousness of Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe disappearance
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,8,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,9,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,10,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,11,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,15,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,17,FThe inquest resumed on Monday morning
OL,18,Fwith evidence from a further police
OL,19,Fwitness.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
