FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773144740
OL,3,CPolice 'gripped' seriousness of Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe disappearance
OL,6,FMr Robinson said he had carried out a
OL,7,Fcompliance review in 2020 into the
OL,8,Fpolice handling of the Noah Donohoe
OL,9,Fcase.
OL,11,FThe witness told the jury he had
OL,12,Fidentified five areas of non-
OL,13,Fcompliance with PSNI procedures,
OL,14,Fincluding around the recording of risk
OL,15,Fassessments.
OL,17,FHe also referred to a more detailed
OL,18,Freview of the case that had been
OL,19,Fcarried out by another inspector in
OL,20,FAugust 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773144740
OL,3,CPolice 'gripped' seriousness of Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe disappearance
OL,6,FHe said the "overall case" in this
OL,7,Freview was that there had been a "very
OL,8,Fgood response to the investigation".
OL,10,FHe said: "To be clear, I agree with
OL,11,Fthe general thrust of the report that
OL,12,Fit was a good response."
OL,14,FThe witness said the seriousness of
OL,15,Fthe investigation had been "gripped at
OL,16,Fan early stage" by police.
OL,18,FHe said: "A large amount of police
OL,19,Fresources were engaged at a very early
OL,20,Fstage."
