OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773144740
OL,3,CPolice 'gripped' seriousness of Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe disappearance
OL,6,FThe officer said he did not consider
OL,7,Fthere would have been any benefit to
OL,8,Fhaving a senior investigating officer
OL,9,F(SIO) appointed to the case at an
OL,10,Fearlier stage.
OL,12,FCounsel for the coroner, Declan Quinn,
OL,13,Fasked Mr Robinson if he believed any
OL,14,Fof the issues raised in the review
OL,15,F"affected the speed or the quality of
OL,16,Fthe search for Noah".
OL,18,FThe officer replied: "I don't believe
OL,19,Fso."
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@TO]zD@VOU{D@DO]
